        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Promoting Programming, Research, Education and Preservation in Civics and Government Act or the PREP Civics and Government Act</strong></p> <p>This bill amends the National Foundation on the Arts and the Humanities Act of 1965 to include the study and interpretation of civics and government under the definition of humanities. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
